</div>
', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('d1d40c80-7842-41f0-bbc0-8eb869fcaa20', '7f093f33-acba-4966-abad-b6bbb4b635e6', 'fillup', 'Questions 31-40', '<div class="s-block-item s-repeatable-item s-block-sortable-item s-blog-post-section blog-section">
<div class="container">
<div class="sixteen columns">
<div class="s-blog-section-inner">
<div class="s-component s-text ">
<div class="">
<div class="s-component-content s-font-body">
<p>Complete the notes below</p>
<p>Write <strong>ONE WORD ONLY</strong> for each answer.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="s-block-item s-repeatable-item s-block-sortable-item s-blog-post-section blog-section">
<div class="container">
<div class="sixteen columns">
<div class="s-blog-section-inner">
<div class="s-component s-text ">
<div class="">
<p class="s-component-content s-font-body"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong>New engineering designs: Scottish case study</strong></span></p>
<p class="s-component-content s-font-body"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Project to renovate and link two canals in Scotland</span></p>
<p class="s-component-content s-font-body"><strong>Historical background</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="s-block-item s-repeatable-item s-block-sortable-item s-blog-post-section blog-section">
<div class="container">
<div class="sixteen columns">
<div class="s-blog-section-inner">
<div class="s-component s-text ">
<div class="">
<div class="s-component-content s-font-body">
<ul>
<li>1790: opening of the Forth and Clyde Canal (Scotland’s {oldest} canal)</li>
<li>1822: opening of the Union Canal</li>
<li>The two canals allowed boats to cross the {central} part of Scotland</li>
<li>Locks (steps) connected the two canals near Falkirk</li>
<li>1842: competition from a new {railway}</li>
<li>1930s: the locks were demolished</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Millennium project</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Aim: to improve Scotland’s {transport}</li>
<li>The long-term goal – to strengthen the Scottish {economy}</li>
<li>Involved restoration of the two canals</li>
<li>Problem: one canal is 35m lower than the other</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>The Falkirk Wheel (a mechanical lift)</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Completed in 2002</li>
<li>Two large tanks are attached to the ends of an arm</li>
<li>The tanks are designed to remain in a {horizontal} position.</li>
<li>A boat sails into each tank</li>
<li>The weight of the tanks with their contents is always {equal}</li>
<li>Little energy is needed to rotate the arm</li>
<li>Visual quality – resembles a {sculpture}</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Manufacturing</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All the parts were constructed off-site</li>
<li>1,200 tonnes of {steel} were used</li>
<li>Joints were bolted and welded to reduce the effects of {stress}</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">PART 4: NEW ENGINEERING DESIGNS – SCOTTISH CASE STUDY</strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Lecturer:</strong> Good morning everyone. In the last lecture, we discussed innovation in engineering design, and today I want to look at a case study. I’ll be talking about an engineering project which was recently carried out in Scotland to restore two old waterways—canals in fact—and then link them together.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\">I’ll talk about the design features, but first, I’ll tell you a little bit about the historical background of the project. One of these canals, called the Forth and Clyde, opened in 1790, and it’s the <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"201\">(31) oldest</strong></span> of Scotland’s canals. The other, the Union Canal, opened in 1822.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Although the two canals were built at different levels, together they enabled vessels to travel from west to east across <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"121\">(32) central</strong></span> Scotland. This is because the canals were connected near a town called Falkirk by a complicated system of locks, which have steps and gates allowing boats to move from one level to another.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\">However, from 1842, the two canals faced serious competition when the <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"70\">(33) railway</strong></span> opened, which served the same cross-country route. After that, their use declined steadily, and in the 1930s, the locks at Falkirk were demolished.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">THE MILLENNIUM PROJECT</strong></h3>\n<p id=\"p-rc_75e4fd8b36b34943-50\" data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Lecturer:</strong> Times change, however. Moving on now to the turn of the millennium, Scotland embarked on an ambitious new project. The aim was to upgrade the country’s infrastructure, especially in the area of <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"204\">(34) transport</strong></span> there was a multi million pound budget for this. It was a very big investment indeed, and in fact, the whole project was just one part of a long-term plan which had been developed to stimulate the national <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"377\">(35) economy</strong></span>. <span class=\"citation-163 citation-end-163\">And amongst other things, it involved restoring the two old canals and bringing them back into use.</span><button class=\"button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details for citation from IELTS Song Ngữ 🎉. Opens side panel.\" data-hveid=\"0\" data-ved=\"0CAAQvoAQahgKEwi27a3CyICTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQmQI\"></button></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\">However, there was one major challenge. As I mentioned just now, the Forth and Clyde Canal lies below the level of the Union Canal. There’s a 35m difference, and the locks had been destroyed. So the problem was how to get boats from one level to the other.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">THE FALKIRK WHEEL (MECHANICAL LIFT)</strong></h3>\n<p id=\"p-rc_75e4fd8b36b34943-51\" data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Lecturer:</strong> Whatever kind of solution was chosen, it was felt that it should be really innovative and imaginative—a fitting way to mark the beginning of a new millennium. <span class=\"citation-162 citation-end-162\">The resulting structure was a mechanical lift for boats, and because it rotates, it was called the Falkirk Wheel.</span></p>\n<p id=\"p-rc_75e4fd8b36b34943-52\" data-path-to-node=\"14\"><span class=\"citation-161 citation-end-161\">The Falkirk Wheel was completed in 2002, and it was the first structure of its kind—an engineering innovation.</span> The structure consists of two very large tanks, each large enough to contain a boat. In fact, these are fixed onto opposite sides of a vertical arm.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\">Basically, what happens is that the arm lowers one boat from the higher canal to the canal below, and at the same time, it raises another boat from the lower canal to the level of the upper canal. How does this work? Well, the tanks are mounted in such a way that they stay in a <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"279\">(36) horizontal</strong></span> plane.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\">As one boat, together with the water that it floats in, sails into the upper tank, another floating boat simultaneously enters the lower tank. The system works on scientific principles which ensure that the weight of each boat plus the water that it floats in will be <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"268\">(37) equal</strong></span> to the other.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\">So once the boats have entered the tank, the arm rotates, and because the tanks are in balance, only a very small amount of energy is required for this rotation. Engineers generally agree that the Falkirk Wheel is highly functional. It’s also visually stunning; it’s an unusual shape, it looks very attractive with a lot of curves. In fact, it almost looks like a <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"364\">(38) sculpture</strong>.</span></p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"18\">\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MANUFACTURING</strong></h3>\n<p id=\"p-rc_75e4fd8b36b34943-53\" data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Lecturer:</strong> So where was the Falkirk Wheel manufactured? Well, it was produced entirely off-site at a place in England, about 370km away. It was constructed from <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"160\">(39) steel</strong></span>—1,200 tonnes of it. It was also very strong. For example, the joints were bolted together as well as being welded. This was because a lot of <span style=\"background-color: #f1c40f;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"312\">(40) stress</strong></span> would be placed on them by the weight of the boats and the water. <span class=\"citation-160 citation-end-160\">Over 15,000 bolts were used, and each one was tightened by hand.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\">Of course, since it’s been in use, the design has been tested on an ongoing basis…</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('06dd26fa-46d3-4f32-a687-1f5913fe1b89', 'cda6a967-c341-4446-9ac6-4d672094ba47', 'radio', 'Questions 1–5', '', '<p>Choose <strong>TRUE</strong> if the statement agrees with the information given in the text, choose <strong>FALSE</strong> if the statement contradicts the information, or choose <strong>NOT GIVEN</strong> if there is no information on this.</p>', 'true_false_not_given', '[{"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Artwork from ancient Egypt indicates that the use of candles was limited to royalty."}, {"correct": 1, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Tallow was produced exclusively for candle making."}, {"correct": 0, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "In the Middle Ages, candles made from beeswax were more popular than those made from other substances."}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "Keeping time at auctions in the 15th century involved marking lines on the surface of a candle."}, {"correct": 2, "options": [{"option_text": "TRUE"}, {"option_text": "FALSE"}, {"option_text": "NOT GIVEN"}], "question": "The candles used at auctions had to be of good quality."}]', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">1. Artwork from ancient Egypt indicates that the use of candles was limited to royalty. — {FALSE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"4\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng câu tốt nhất:</strong></p>\n<blockquote data-path-to-node=\"4,0,1\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4,0,1,0\"><em data-path-to-node=\"4,0,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">“Ancient Egyptian artworks depict the use of candles by writers and philosophers who worked long after sundown.”</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,0,0\">Câu hỏi khẳng định rằng tác phẩm nghệ thuật từ Ai Cập cổ đại chỉ ra việc sử dụng nến <strong data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"85\">bị giới hạn chỉ dành cho giới hoàng tộc</strong> (<em data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"126\">limited to royalty</em>).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,1,0\">Tuy nhiên, bài đọc viết rất rõ ràng: các tác phẩm nghệ thuật Ai Cập cổ đại khắc họa việc nến được sử dụng bởi <strong data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"110\">các nhà văn và nhà triết học</strong> (<em data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"140\">writers and philosophers</em>) để làm việc muộn sau khi mặt trời lặn.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,2,0\">Do thông tin về đối tượng sử dụng trong bài đọc mâu thuẫn trực tiếp với từ hạn định tuyệt đối <em data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"94\">\"limited to royalty\"</em> của câu hỏi, đáp án chính xác bắt buộc phải là <strong data-path-to-node=\"4,1,1,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"162\">FALSE</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">2. Tallow was produced exclusively for candle making. — {FALSE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"10\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 1):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"...tallow, the white, nearly tasteless fat of cattle or sheep <strong data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"83\">also used to make soap</strong>.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Từ khóa <strong data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"exclusively\"</strong> (duy nhất/độc quyền) làm câu này sai. Bài đọc khẳng định mỡ động vật (tallow) còn được dùng để làm xà phòng (soap).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">3. In the Middle Ages, candles made from beeswax were more popular than those made from other substances. — {TRUE}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"12\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 2):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"A major improvement... came in the Middle Ages, when <strong data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">beeswax was preferred over animal or vegetable fats</strong>...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Từ \"preferred over\" (được ưa chuộng hơn) đồng nghĩa với \"more popular\". Người thời Trung Cổ chuộng sáp ong hơn mỡ động vật hay thực vật vì nó có mùi dễ chịu và sạch sẽ hơn.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">4. Keeping time at auctions in the 15th century involved marking lines on the surface of a candle. — {NOT GIVEN}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"14\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 2):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"At auctions, the bidding time was limited by <strong data-path-to-node=\"14,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"66\">inserting a pin into a candle</strong> and letting the wax melt until the pin dropped...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Cách đo thời gian được mô tả là cắm một chiếc đinh ghim (pin) vào nến. Bài đọc <strong data-path-to-node=\"14,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"91\">không nhắc gì</strong> đến việc đánh dấu các đường kẻ (marking lines) trên bề mặt nến.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">5. The candles used at auctions had to be of good quality. — {NOT GIVEN}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"16\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 2):</strong> Đoạn này chỉ nói về mục đích dùng nến để kết thúc phiên đấu giá khi cái ghim rơi xuống.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Bài đọc <strong data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">không đưa ra thông tin</strong> hay yêu cầu nào về chất lượng (good quality) của những cây nến được sử dụng trong các buổi đấu giá này.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('81b4a919-67b5-4c5f-8cdc-97318f268336', '68dd49fe-cbe8-49fb-8990-9548bc8f0098', 'fillup', 'Questions 23-26', '<p><span lang="EN-US">Complete the summary below.</span></p>
<p><span lang="EN-US">Write</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span><span lang="EN-US"><strong>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS AND/OR A NUMBER </strong></span><span lang="EN-US">from</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span><span lang="EN-US">the</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span><span lang="EN-US">passage</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span><span lang="EN-US">for</span><span lang="EN-US"> </span><span lang="EN-US">each </span>answer.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-US">James Flynn</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span lang="EN-US">During the  {Mid-1980s}  , James Flynn conducted research showing that IQ scores were increasing. Flynn then analysed specific kinds of reasoning ability separately. He found that tests called { Raven’s matrices }  , which measured visuo-spatial skills, accounted for the biggest score increases, whereas scores in numerical and {Verbal}   components rose less steeply. Results from research in other  {Countries}  , which Flynn has examined more recently, are consistent with his earlier findings.</span></p>', NULL, 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<ul>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">23. During the {mid-1980s}, James Flynn conducted research showing that IQ scores were increasing.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “James Flynn… first showed that IQ scores were rising in the <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">mid-1980s</strong>…” (Dòng đầu đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đây là mốc thời gian Flynn bắt đầu công bố phát hiện về sự gia tăng điểm số IQ.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">24. Flynn then analysed specific kinds of reasoning ability separately. He found that tests called {Raven’s matrices}, which measured visuo-spatial skills, accounted for the biggest score increases…</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “This last test category usually includes ‘<strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"54\">Raven’s matrices</strong>‘… The strongest gains in almost every case were on Raven’s matrices and similar tests…” (Đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> “Biggest score increases” trong đề bài tương ứng với “Strongest gains” trong bài đọc. Đây là tên loại bài tập trắc nghiệm hình ảnh dùng để đo lường khả năng tư duy không gian.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">25. …whereas scores in numerical and {verbal} components rose less steeply.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…while <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"21\">verbal</strong> and arithmetical scores showed more modest rises.” (Đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đề bài dùng “numerical” thay cho “arithmetical” (thuộc về số học), và “rose less steeply” thay cho “modest rises” (tăng khiêm tốn). Từ còn thiếu ở đây là <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"166\">verbal</strong> (ngôn ngữ).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">26. Results from research in other {countries}, which Flynn has examined more recently, are consistent with his earlier findings.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “Since presenting his original paper, Flynn has looked at data from further <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"87\">countries</strong> and found the same upward trend…” (Dòng cuối đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sau nghiên cứu ban đầu tại 14 quốc gia, Flynn tiếp tục xem xét dữ liệu từ nhiều <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"92\">quốc gia</strong> khác và thu được kết quả đồng nhất.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('5a836ed2-d532-4bc6-a43f-4583e5371c11', 'cda6a967-c341-4446-9ac6-4d672094ba47', 'fillup', 'Questions 6–13', '<p>Complete the notes below.</p>
<p>Write<strong> ONE WORD ONLY</strong> from the passage for each answer.</p>
<h4 data-path-to-node="4"><strong data-path-to-node="4" data-index-in-node="0">Candle making</strong></h4>
<p data-path-to-node="5"><strong data-path-to-node="5" data-index-in-node="0">Advantages of the various types of wax used in candlemaking</strong></p>
<ul data-path-to-node="6">
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="6,0,0">beeswax made less { mess} than animal fats</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="6,1,0">spermaceti wax produced a stronger {light}</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="6,2,0">ozokerite did not melt when the {weather} was hot</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="6,3,0">paraffin blend made good quality candles which were inexpensive</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-path-to-node="7"><strong data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="0">The candlemaking process</strong></p>
<ul data-path-to-node="8">
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="8,0,0">in the dipping method, wicks were made from rushes</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="8,1,0">in the pouring method, melted beeswax was poured over a wick that was made of {cotton}</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-path-to-node="9"><strong data-path-to-node="9" data-index-in-node="0">Candlemaking today</strong></p>
<ul data-path-to-node="10">
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="10,0,0">wax can be obtained from the stem of a {shrub} called candelilla</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="10,1,0">bayberry wax, used in decorative candles, comes from the plant’s {fruit}</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="10,2,0">the {casing} of a decorative candle is made from wax which can resist heat</p>
</li>
<li>
<p data-path-to-node="10,3,0">{wire} is often used to keep the wick of a candle upright</p>
</li>
</ul>', '', 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">6. mess — {beeswax made less mess than animal fats}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 2):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"Beeswax was preferred... because it smelled pleasant and <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"78\">did not produce as much mess</strong> as other fats.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Cụm \"did not produce as much\" đồng nghĩa với \"made less\". Sáp ong sạch hơn mỡ động vật vì nó không tạo ra nhiều vết bẩn/sự bừa bộn (<strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"144\">mess</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">7. light — {spermaceti wax produced a stronger light}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 3):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"Spermaceti wax was popular because it provided a <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"70\">significantly brighter light</strong>...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> \"Brighter light\" tương ứng với \"stronger light\" (ánh sáng mạnh/sáng hơn).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">8. weather — {ozokerite did not melt when the weather was hot}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 3):</strong> *\"Ozokerite... was also popular... particularly in <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"71\">warmer weather</strong>, khi điểm nóng chảy cao giúp nó <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"118\">remained firm</strong> [không bị chảy/luôn cứng].\" *</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Nhờ điểm nóng chảy cao, Ozokerite không bị chảy khi thời tiết (<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"75\">weather</strong>) nóng.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">9. cotton — {melted beeswax was poured over a wick that was made of cotton}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 5):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"In the pouring method... melted beeswax was poured over a suspended <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"89\">cotton wick</strong>...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Trong phương pháp đổ (pouring), bấc nến được làm bằng sợi bông (<strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"76\">cotton</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">10. shrub — {wax can be obtained from the stem of a shrub called candelilla}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"13\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 7):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"...candelilla, which comes from the <strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"57\">stem of the candelilla shrub</strong>...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sáp candelilla được lấy từ thân (stem) của một loại cây bụi (<strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"73\">shrub</strong>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">11. fruit — {bayberry wax... comes from the plant’s fruit}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"15\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 8):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"One example is bayberry wax, which is <strong data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"59\">derived from the fruit</strong> of the bayberry bush...\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sáp bayberry được chiết xuất từ quả (<strong data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">fruit</strong>) của cây bayberry.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">12. casing — {the casing of a decorative candle is made from wax which can resist heat}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"17\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 8):</strong> *\"In decorative candles, non-burning wax is used to make the <strong data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"81\">casing</strong>, which is <strong data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"98\">not intended to melt</strong> [resist heat].\" *</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Phần vỏ ngoài (<strong data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">casing</strong>) của nến trang trí làm từ sáp không cháy để chịu nhiệt, không bị tan chảy khi nến cháy bên trong.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">13. wire — {wire is often used to keep the wick of a candle upright}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"19\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng (Đoạn 9):</strong> <em data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">\"Often, these wicks have a <strong data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"47\">center made of wire</strong> that allows them to... <strong data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"90\">remain erect</strong> [upright] in the melted wax.\"</em></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sợi dây kim loại (<strong data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"30\">wire</strong>) được đặt ở lõi bấc để giúp nó luôn đứng thẳng (<strong data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"83\">upright/erect</strong>) khi sáp tan chảy.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('784259f6-fffe-44e0-80d1-6e0ebde148bd', 'e9077a22-fe21-4bd1-b132-e534d733fb11', 'matrix', 'Questions 14-18', '', '<p>Match each statement with the correct person, <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="121">A, B, C</strong> or <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="132">D</strong>.</p>
<p>Choose the correct letter, <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="162">A, B, C</strong> or <strong data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="173">D</strong>, in boxes 14-18.</p>', 'choose_a_title', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "standard", "legendTitle": "List of people", "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "Modern technology has influenced some aspects of human intelligence.", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "IQ scores may not have attained their natural limit.", "correctCategoryLetter": "D"}, {"itemText": "Improved diet has a positive effect on mental powers", "correctCategoryLetter": "C"}, {"itemText": "Exceptional individuals can have an impact on collective intelligence.", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}, {"itemText": "As societies become more sophisticated the need for problem-solving skills increases.", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "James Flynn", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "John Rust", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "Robert Howard", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "Thomas Teasdale", "categoryLetter": "D"}]}', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">14. Modern technology has influenced some aspects of human intelligence — {A} James Flynn</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “<strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"12\">Flynn</strong> believes that demands of <strong data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"43\">visuo-spatial abilities have grown because of TV, computers and cars</strong>…” (Đoạn C)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Flynn cho rằng các thiết bị công nghệ hiện đại đã thúc đẩy khả năng thị giác – không gian của con người.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">15. IQ scores may not have attained their natural limit — {D} Thomas Teasdale</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…as <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"18\">Teasdale</strong> points out, if such a <strong data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">ceiling [natural limit] had been reached</strong>, the test results should show scores pushing against it rather than actually falling.” (Đoạn E)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Teasdale lập luận rằng nếu điểm số thực sự chạm trần (giới hạn tự nhiên), chúng sẽ duy trì ở mức cao thay vì sụt giảm như dữ liệu tại Đan Mạch.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">16. Improved diet has a positive effect on mental powers — {C} Robert Howard</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"9\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"15\">Robert Howard</strong>, argue that overall Intelligence really has risen, helped by <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"90\">better nutrition</strong>…” (Đoạn D)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Howard tin rằng sự cải thiện về dinh dưỡng (nutrition/diet) là một trong những yếu tố giúp tăng trí thông minh.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">17. Exceptional individuals can have an impact on collective intelligence — {B} John Rust</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"11\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “<strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"12\">John Rust</strong>… points out that if just <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"49\">one mind grasps a new concept, such as Einstein</strong>… it may then be easier for <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"126\">society in general</strong> to think in a more complex way.” (Đoạn D)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Rust lấy ví dụ về Einstein để minh họa việc một cá nhân xuất chúng có thể thay đổi cách tư duy của cả cộng đồng.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">18. As societies become more sophisticated the need for problem-solving skills increases — {B} John Rust</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"13\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “<strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"12\">John Rust</strong>… suggests that… in <strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">more complex societies</strong>, people have to <strong data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"84\">think harder to find solutions to problems</strong> they face.” (Đoạn D)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Xã hội càng phức tạp (sophisticated/complex) thì con người càng phải tư duy nhiều hơn để giải quyết vấn đề.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('f2b2d4bd-1624-46a5-a62d-8c9217e6dbad', 'e9077a22-fe21-4bd1-b132-e534d733fb11', 'matrix', 'Questions 19-22', '', '<p class="MsoBodyText"><span lang="EN-US">Which paragraph contains the following information?</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">Choose the correct letter, <strong>A-F, </strong>in boxes 19-22</span><span lang="EN-US">.</span></p>', 'choose_a_title', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "simple", "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "an account of a selection procedure involving a particular group of people", "correctCategoryLetter": "E"}, {"itemText": "a description of one component of a visuo-spatial test", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}, {"itemText": " an overview of the different interpretations of IQ score trends", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "an example of the negative effect affluence may have on IQ trends", "correctCategoryLetter": "F"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "A", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "B", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "C", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "D", "categoryLetter": "D"}, {"categoryText": "E", "categoryLetter": "E"}, {"categoryText": "F", "categoryLetter": "F"}]}', '[{"content": "<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">19. an account of a selection procedure involving a particular group of people — {E}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"17\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “The <strong data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">Danish military</strong> still summons virtually all <strong data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"60\">young men</strong> before a draft board to identify who is suitable to do military service.” (Đoạn E)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đây là quy trình tuyển quân của Đan Mạch áp dụng cho một nhóm đối tượng cụ thể (thanh niên 17 tuổi).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">20. a description of one component of a visuo-spatial test — {B}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"19\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…’<strong data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">Raven’s matrices</strong>‘ – sequential patterns with <strong data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"61\">one piece missing</strong>. The candidate has to choose… which shape to put in the empty space.” (Đoạn B)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đoạn B mô tả chi tiết cách thức hoạt động của bài test Raven – một phần của kiểm tra thị giác – không gian.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">21. an overview of the different interpretations of IQ score trends — {A}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"21\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…psychologists <strong data-path-to-node=\"21,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"29\">disagree</strong> about what the upward trend in scores really means. <strong data-path-to-node=\"21,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"90\">Some</strong> researchers argue… <strong data-path-to-node=\"21,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"116\">Others</strong> say…” (Đoạn A)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đoạn mở đầu đưa ra cái nhìn tổng quan về các luồng ý kiến khác nhau đối với xu hướng tăng điểm IQ.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">22. an example of the negative effect affluence may have on IQ trends — {F}</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"23\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…dramatic Improvements in mental ability disappear as societies become <strong data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"85\">more prosperous</strong>. …<strong data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"105\">prosperity often led to decadence</strong>, and argues that the case of <strong data-path-to-node=\"23,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"168\">ancient Rome</strong>…” (Đoạn F)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Flynn đặt giả thuyết rằng sự thịnh vượng (affluence/prosperity) có thể dẫn đến sự suy đồi (decadence) và làm giảm tốc độ phát triển trí tuệ.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('46b2aeaf-ddb2-4d1a-b95c-527aea8ab5ef', 'e9077a22-fe21-4bd1-b132-e534d733fb11', 'fillup', 'Questions 23-26', '<p>Complete the summary below.</p>
<p>Write <strong>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> from the passage for each answer.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-US">James Flynn</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span lang="EN-US">During the  {Mid-1980s}  , James Flynn conducted research showing that IQ scores were increasing. Flynn then analysed specific kinds of reasoning ability separately. He found that tests called { Raven’s matrices }  , which measured visuo-spatial skills, accounted for the biggest score increases, whereas scores in numerical and {Verbal}   components rose less steeply. Results from research in other  {Countries}  , which Flynn has examined more recently, are consistent with his earlier findings.</span></p>', '', 'short_answer', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<ul>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">23. During the {mid-1980s}, James Flynn conducted research showing that IQ scores were increasing.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “James Flynn… first showed that IQ scores were rising in the <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"74\">mid-1980s</strong>…” (Dòng đầu đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,0,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đây là mốc thời gian Flynn bắt đầu công bố phát hiện về sự gia tăng điểm số IQ.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">24. Flynn then analysed specific kinds of reasoning ability separately. He found that tests called {Raven’s matrices}, which measured visuo-spatial skills, accounted for the biggest score increases…</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “This last test category usually includes ‘<strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"54\">Raven’s matrices</strong>‘… The strongest gains in almost every case were on Raven’s matrices and similar tests…” (Đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,1,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> “Biggest score increases” trong đề bài tương ứng với “Strongest gains” trong bài đọc. Đây là tên loại bài tập trắc nghiệm hình ảnh dùng để đo lường khả năng tư duy không gian.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">25. …whereas scores in numerical and {verbal} components rose less steeply.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “…while <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"21\">verbal</strong> and arithmetical scores showed more modest rises.” (Đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Đề bài dùng “numerical” thay cho “arithmetical” (thuộc về số học), và “rose less steeply” thay cho “modest rises” (tăng khiêm tốn). Từ còn thiếu ở đây là <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,2,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"166\">verbal</strong> (ngôn ngữ).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,3,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">26. Results from research in other {countries}, which Flynn has examined more recently, are consistent with his earlier findings.</strong></p>\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1\">\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,0,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Dẫn chứng:</strong> “Since presenting his original paper, Flynn has looked at data from further <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"87\">countries</strong> and found the same upward trend…” (Dòng cuối đoạn B).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,1,0\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Giải thích:</strong> Sau nghiên cứu ban đầu tại 14 quốc gia, Flynn tiếp tục xem xét dữ liệu từ nhiều <strong data-path-to-node=\"3,3,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"92\">quốc gia</strong> khác và thu được kết quả đồng nhất.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}]', 2);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('0d20a10d-6ff9-42ad-ac78-73d864710aa4', '862bdbbf-6b9e-4dbe-9937-2d6ea7e2f957', 'matching', 'Questions 11–14', '', '<p dir="ltr">What does the speaker say about each of the following volunteer roles at the school fair?</p>
<p dir="ltr">Choose <strong>FOUR </strong>correct answers, <strong>A-F,</strong> next to questions 11-14.</p>', 'summary_completion', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "summary", "summaryText": "<p>Entertainment co-ordinator {This role will mainly involve evening work.}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Advertising and promotion co-ordinator {More than one person is needed for this role.}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Technical co-ordinator {To do this role you need your own transport.}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Staffing co-ordinator {This is a new role for this year’s fair.}</p>", "answerOptions": [{"optionText": "An office will be provided for this role."}, {"optionText": "More than one person is needed for this role."}, {"optionText": "This is a new role for this year’s fair."}, {"optionText": "This role will start next month."}, {"optionText": "This role will mainly involve evening work."}, {"optionText": "To do this role you need your own transport."}], "matchingItems": []}', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\">PART 2: KENVALE SCHOOL FAIR</h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Good evening, and thank you for coming to the Kenvale School Fair volunteers meeting.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> As you know, this is the biggest fundraising event in the school year, and as usual we’re expecting lots of people to come, which is why we’re starting to prepare now, six months before the big day.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> I’ll begin tonight by talking about the different volunteer roles so you can decide what you’d like to do.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The entertainment coordinator position involves deciding what kinds of rides and activities will be at the fair and making sure there’s a good variety of things to do.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> From past experience, this role involves a lot of liaising with other helpers and the entertainers, which means that <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong>(11) E (most of the work is done after office hours).</strong></span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> We need an advertising and promotion coordinator to make sure that people hear about the fair and lots of people come.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> We know this is a big job, so we’ve decided to have <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\">(12) B (a couple of people doing it to share the load).</span></strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The parent who did this role last year has just been offered a job which starts next month, so she won’t be able to lend us the benefit of her experience sadly.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The technical coordinator makes sure that there is a suitable stage for the performers and that there are enough speakers and people can hear them and so on.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Now, this may sound like a technical background is required, but it’s not as you don’t actually have to set up or fix anything yourself.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Having <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\">(13) F (a car is essential though) </span></strong></span>because in the week leading up to the event you’ll need to be able to get to the school early in the mornings and occasionally later at night.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> We also need a Staffing Coordinator. This person will be required to look after the many helpers on the day of the fair.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\">(14) C (This role has just been created)</span> </strong>based on our experience of last year’s event.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> We found that our volunteers felt a bit overworked and so we’re hoping that this role will make things easier. It will help to reduce stress if you organise the helpers about a month before the fair.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Now moving on to the map of the school fair, I’ll point out some of the more important areas that you’ll need to know about so you can help direct the visitors.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> You can see that we’ll be using the large grounds just behind the school and we’ll set up temporary areas and pathways there.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The first thing I’ll show you are the fairground rides which are always popular with the children.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong> If you look at the map, you’ll see the fair entrance at the bottom. From there, follow the main path in the direction of the river and it’s the third area on the left, the large rectangular area (15) I.</strong></span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The entertainment stage is a big feature of the fair and this is where everyone will be able to see all the performers.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"23\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong>To find this go straight along the main path until you get to the river, turn right and follow the path to the end and there it is (16) D.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"24\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> There’s not much shade here so we should remind parents to bring hats for their children.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> If anyone wants a cold drink or a snack then they’ll ask you where the cafe is.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Originally we were going to put it opposite the toilets but we’ve decided to put it near the river to take advantage of the views and breezes.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">You can see it on the map, it’s a circular area surrounded by trees near the playground (17) A.</span></strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The first aid tent is always an important part of the fair. We wanted to put that in an area that was easily accessible and a bit separated from the other attractions but near the entrance.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong> If you look at the map, you’ll see it south of the toilets, not far from the school fence line (18) H.</strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> The market stalls are where visitors will be able to pick up a bargain or some homemade produce.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"31\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Last year these were located just south of the meeting area but the stall holders complained that it was too exposed and hot.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> <span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">So this year we’ve moved them to the north of the meeting area, lots of good shelter provided by the trees here (19) E.</span></strong></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Of course there’ll be the ever popular pony rides.<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffe786;\"><strong> To reach these direct visitors to follow the main path from the entrance until they reach the L-shaped area on the left next to the playground (20) B.</strong></span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Principal:</strong> Now as I was saying…</p>"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('b8750631-dbac-4b4b-bda2-b7953bd49243', '862bdbbf-6b9e-4dbe-9937-2d6ea7e2f957', 'matrix', 'Questions 15–20', NULL, '<p>Label the map below</p>
<p>Choose the correct letter, <strong>A</strong>–<strong>I,</strong> next to questions 15-20.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," width="398" height="374" loading="lazy"></p>
', 'other', 'null', 'null', 'null', '{"layoutType": "simple", "legendTitle": null, "matrixItems": [{"itemText": "Fairground rides", "correctCategoryLetter": "I"}, {"itemText": "Entertainment stage", "correctCategoryLetter": "D"}, {"itemText": "Café", "correctCategoryLetter": "A"}, {"itemText": "First aid tent", "correctCategoryLetter": "H"}, {"itemText": "Market stalls", "correctCategoryLetter": "E"}, {"itemText": "Pony rides", "correctCategoryLetter": "B"}], "matrixCategories": [{"categoryText": "A", "categoryLetter": "A"}, {"categoryText": "B", "categoryLetter": "B"}, {"categoryText": "C", "categoryLetter": "C"}, {"categoryText": "D", "categoryLetter": "D"}, {"categoryText": "E", "categoryLetter": "E"}, {"categoryText": "F", "categoryLetter": "F"}, {"categoryText": "G", "categoryLetter": "G"}, {"categoryText": "H", "categoryLetter": "H"}, {"categoryText": "I", "categoryLetter": "I"}]}', '[{"content": "<p>1</p>\n"}]', 1);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('55737d17-5990-4c4e-aa20-773566e04bff', '1db00fa5-d788-4fed-a36c-fb036a348610', 'fillup', 'Questions 1–10', '<p>Complete the table below.<br />Write <strong>ONE WORD AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Asia-Pacific Tours Activity Holidays</strong></p>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; width: 80.0063%; height: 212.177px;" border="1" cellpadding="0">
<thead>
<tr style="height: 22.9271px;">
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 13.2981%;">
<p><strong>Tour</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 70.6899%;">
<p><strong>Details</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 15.9227%;">
<p><strong>Cost</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 42.0938px;">
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 13.2981%;">
<p><strong>Example</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 70.6899%;">
<p>• a cookery course at a 5-star hotel</p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 15.9227%;"> </td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 42.5208px;">
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 13.2981%;">
<p><strong>Vietnam</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 70.6899%;">
<p>• either {diving} lessons or a one-day trek in the {jungle}</p>
<p>• attend a {dance} performance</p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 15.9227%;">
<p>£ {1450}</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 62.1146px;">
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 13.2981%;">
<p><strong>Hong Kong</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 70.6899%;">
<p>• go to the hills to look at {birds} in a country park</p>
<p>• followed by {dinner} in a monastery</p>
<p>• visit an {electronics} factory with the chance to shop</p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 15.9227%;">
<p>£1,320</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 42.5208px;">
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 13.2981%;">
<p><strong> {Japan}</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 70.6899%;">
<p>• visit a museum of traditional {costume}</p>
<p>• tour of a big {fish } market</p>
</td>
<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt; width: 15.9227%;">
<p>£1,800</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
', NULL, 'gap_filling', 'null', 'null', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">SECTION 1: ASIA-PACIFIC TOURS ACTIVITY HOLIDAYS</strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"8\">Agent:</strong> Asia Pacific tours can I help you?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"50\">Woman:</strong> Yes, I’ve been looking at your website and I’d like some more information about your activity holidays.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"161\">Agent:</strong> Certainly. You know of course the prices of the tours include stays in 3 star hotels and they include airfares.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"280\">Woman:</strong> Great. What about your tour of <strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"318\">Vietnam</strong>? My sister went there last year and loved it.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"5\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Yes, it’s a really beautiful place and probably our fastest growing destination. Now that package includes several opportunities to take courses.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Don&#8217;t you have a cookery course of some kind?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> We certainly do. If you love eating out in Vietnam, like most people do, and want to know how to prepare a meal, you can learn how from a master in a 5 star hotel. On another day you have a choice of two activities.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\">The first is instruction in <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"28\">(1) diving</strong></span> in the South China Sea. Not a certificate course but just an introduction. Most people think it’s wonderful.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\">Or if you want to stay dry but still want some exercise, you can spend the day on a trek through the <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"101\">(2) jungle</strong></span> near the beach. It’s not difficult and everyone seems to enjoy it.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Anything cultural on offer?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"12\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> We used to take people to a Vietnamese opera, but that didn’t prove so popular.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\">So now we include a <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">(3) dance</strong></span> show, and our clients all rave about that. They say the colours are just magnificent.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Hmm, what’s the cost?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"15\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> I’ve just noticed it’s now a special price. The holiday used to be £1,600,</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\">but it’s just been reduced to £<span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"31\">(4) 1,450</strong></span>. So you do save quite a bit. And as I said, it seems to be our up and coming tour.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"17\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Well, let’s see. Perhaps you could tell me a little about the Hong Kong tour. I noticed it includes a walk in the hills of one of their country parks where you have the chance to see<span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"> <strong data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"190\">(5) birds</strong> </span>of all sorts.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Yes, that’s a very popular activity. People don’t realize that Hong Kong isn’t just a crowded city. That’s a half day activity, and you go with a trained escort.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">And it includes <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"20\" data-index-in-node=\"16\">(6) dinner</strong></span> in a monastery where you end your day.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\">And then, we wouldn’t want you to miss out altogether on shopping, so there’s another day</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\">when we take you round an <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"22\" data-index-in-node=\"26\">(7) electronics</strong></span> factory. Now that might sound like an odd thing to do, but it’s actually really fascinating, and not like your usual ceramics factory. And you can buy their products there quite cheaply.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\">Now, the whole Hong Kong package is just £1,320 per person.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"24\">\n<p data-path-to-node=\"25\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"25\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">(Questions 8-10)</strong></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Sounds interesting.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"26\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong>But let me find out about one more place. I’ve always wanted to go to Korea, but not on this trip and I’ve been to Thailand which I loved,</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"27\">but what about your <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"27\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">(8) Japan</strong></span> package?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"28\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Good choice. Well, that tour includes a terrific trip to a museum of traditional <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"28\" data-index-in-node=\"88\">(9) costume</strong></span>. The exhibits are gorgeous. They’ve got an absolutely priceless collection.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"29\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"29\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> And I think the website says you take your clients to a market, don’t you? A crafts market, I think.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"30\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> Well, we do go to a market but it’s one that sells <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"30\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">(10) fish</strong></span>, and it’s one of the largest in the world.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"31\">And you have the chance to sample the wares in a little restaurant nearby. We also give you plenty of free time to wander around the city with our guides if you want.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"32\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> And what’s the cost of all that?</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"33\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"33\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> £1,800.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"34\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"34\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Well you’ve been ever so helpful. I’ve noted all the details down and I’ll get back to you when I’ve made up my mind.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"35\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"35\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agent:</strong> If we can give you any more help, do ring back.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"36\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"36\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Woman:</strong> Thanks, I will.</p>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('79922264-56b2-4fa2-a57e-18e2870eff3b', '7e7e79e8-abcd-4257-9716-7822f75ee77d', 'checkbox', 'Questions 11–12', NULL, '<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, A–E.</p>
<p>Which <strong>TWO </strong>items will participants on the dancing course receive when they check in?</p>
', 'multiple_choice_many', 'null', '[{"option": "a class list", "correct": true}, {"option": "a face towel", "correct": false}, {"option": "a name tag", "correct": false}, {"option": "a shoe bag", "correct": true}, {"option": "a water bottle", "correct": false}]', 'null', 'null', '[{"content": "<h3 data-path-to-node=\"3\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">SECTION 2: WEEKEND DANCING COURSE WELCOME</strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Organizer:</strong> Hello everyone, and welcome to this weekend dancing course. Nice that you&#8217;re here safely. Since you&#8217;ve all just arrived, I&#8217;d like to tell you firstly a bit about today&#8217;s program and secondly how to get around this community center.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Firstly, straight after this talk, you&#8217;ll go off to the office where you should check in at the registration desk.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"6\">Make sure you&#8217;re wearing the name tags that we posted you out in the mail last week.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"7\">The staff there will give you each a <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>11/12 [D]</strong> <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"37\">cloth bag</strong> as a little present from us, to keep your <strong data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"89\">dancing shoes</strong> in for the weekend.</span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8\">Other things useful to take to class each day will be a bottle of water—hopefully you&#8217;ve all brought one with you—and a towel for your face if it&#8217;s hot and you feel you need one.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>11/12 [A] </strong>Also at registration, you can pick up a <strong data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"40\">list for the level class</strong> that you&#8217;re in, so you can start learning people&#8217;s names.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"10\">After checking in, this first afternoon is free for everyone. You could use this time to start thinking about your costumes for the final show, but we won&#8217;t be making them until tomorrow.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">For those of you who are interested,<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"77\"> (13/14) [D] </strong></span></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\">there&#8217;s a <strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"47\">lecture</strong> this afternoon in the <strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"77\">Main Hall </strong>on the <strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"94\">history of dance</strong>. </span><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">Or you could practice for Sunday&#8217;s concert in the Music Room.</span></span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"77\">(1</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>3/14) [C]</strong><strong>There is also an informal gathering planned for tonight, consisting of mainly easy dances, </strong></span>where you can get to know each other.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"14\">The tests of different levels won&#8217;t be held until the final afternoon, so there&#8217;s no need to worry about those yet.</p>\n<hr data-path-to-node=\"15\">\n<h3 data-path-to-node=\"16\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">MAP DIRECTIONS </strong></h3>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17\">Organizer: Now I said I would tell you how to find your way around the community centre. Well, we&#8217;re standing at the South End of the site.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"18\">I&#8217;ll tell you where the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>[15]</strong> </span></span><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\">bathrooms</span></span> </strong>are first. That’s the most important thing.<strong> </strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">Walk straight ahead from here, pass this first big block on your left, and you&#8217;ll find the bathrooms on your left just after it.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"19\">Now, equally important of course is where you&#8217;ll sleep. So the<strong> <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\">[16] bunk rooms</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"> are just here on our left, beside where we&#8217;re standing now.</span></p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"20\">Now we also have a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>[19] </strong><strong>games room</strong>,</span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"> where you can entertain yourself during your free time. Well, you&#8217;ll get there if you go straight ahead from where we&#8217;re standing now, take the first turning right, and carry on to the second building. It&#8217;s on your right just before the bike racks.</span>Games and books are in the cupboard there, and there&#8217;s a ping pong table, air hockey things like that good for a rainy day.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"21\">Okay, what else? Um, the<strong> <span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\">[18] hall </span></strong>is where we&#8217;ll be for class photos. You can find that in the middle of the site, just south of the music room.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"22\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong>[17] The medical room</strong></span></span>, in case any of you get injured while you&#8217;re dancing, can be found in the center of the site also. Go straight on from here past two pathways, and it&#8217;s on your right beside the music room. The nurse there is very good with sports injuries, so don&#8217;t hesitate to visit her if you need to.</p>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"23\">Any questions? Oh yes,<span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\"><strong> <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">[20] </span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #f3db7b;\">the</span> reception office</strong></span></span>, of course. You&#8217;ll need to go over there after this talk to register. That&#8217;s quite a long walk away from here. Go straight ahead and take the third turning on your right, then you will find that the office is the second building on your left. The staff there are very friendly and if you have any problems during the weekend, go to see them and they&#8217;ll help you out.</p>\n"}]', 0);
INSERT INTO public.questions VALUES ('2f07f20d-44a7-46e1-ab78-d20bedbd6466', '7e7e79e8-abcd-4257-9716-7822f75ee77d', 'checkbox', 'Questions 13-14', NULL, '<p>Choose <strong>TWO </strong>letters, A–E.</p>
<p>Which <strong>TWO </strong>activities will take place on the first afternoon and evening?</p>
